metrics.name: mesos.cpu.utilization
metrics.description: Master percentage of allocated CPUs expressed as ratio [0-1].

metrics.name: mesos.gpu.utilization
metrics.description: Master percentage of allocated GPUs expressed as ratio [0-1].

metrics.name: mesos.mem.utilization
metrics.description: Master percentage of allocated memory expressed as ratio [0-1].

metrics.name: mesos.slaves.active.count
metrics.description: The number of active agents/slaves running for the master.

metrics.name: mesos.slaves.connected.count
metrics.description: The number of agents/slaves connected to the master.

metrics.name: mesos.slaves.disconnected.count
metrics.description: The number of agents/slaves disconnected from the master

metrics.name: mesos.slaves.inactive.count
metrics.description: The number of agents/slaves that are inactive.

metrics.name: mesos.tasks.failed.count
metrics.description: The number of tasks that were failed.

metrics.name: mesos.tasks.finished.count
metrics.description: The number of tasks that were finished.

metrics.name: mesos.uptime
metrics.description: Time master has been up in seconds.

metrics.name: system.load.15m
metrics.description: the average system load during the last 15 minutes expressed as ratio [0-1].
